generalData.homeContent: On the third sunday of the month, a monthly 120 Minute Endurance Race consisting of 1 Hr Practice, 15 Minute Qualify, and a 120 Minute race with 2 mandatory pit-stops to change tyres and fuel. This event is still in construction and will be announced in our discord Chanel when it is completed.
